<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-86-0882 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Sokolov-Ternov-Matveev-Nikishov-Ritus-Baier-Katkov formula for synchrotronradiation is averaged over the field of a cylindrical space charge, neglectingend effects, in connection with the beamstrahlung problem in linear colliders.The result differs slightly from that given recently by Blankenbeclerand Drell. The discrepancy is traced to helicity-flip transitions. (author)8 refs.</TEXT></DOC>